{
  "stem": "10644.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when I came [INAUDIBLE] first time with a pregnancy, and I came to him and I say, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Hauptscharfuhrer, I examined the one, the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and she's pregnant.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when I-- it came, you know-- came, you know, to termination of this pregnancy, I called him and he said, I cannot come.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I understand he was a womanizer, tremendous womanizer with the Latvian-- Latvian women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very happy that he has now a gynecologist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If something happens to these women, he will have a man who will terminate the pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was not [? fetal-- ?] if you have an abortion, it is usually in the first three months.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for example, I had-- let me-- I will give you an example, a classical example.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A classic example-- a German Jewish woman from my camp, from our camp, comes to me and she says, I'm pregnant.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I examine her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's six months pregnant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, tell me where, why did you work?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew already that she had some relations with the German who managed this group of people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Floor ?] [? arbiter, ?] you know, it is-- he didn't work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He only supervised-- supervisor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And probably with him, she became pregnant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She somehow-- I don't know why-- she was hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But six months, she came to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I say, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] all right, we will have to terminate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was not-- not an abortion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That I had to induce labor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that is-- I dilated the cervix.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ruptured the membranes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had between-- [INAUDIBLE] to stimulate the uterus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I brought to-- she had contractions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had labor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she expelled the fetus.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
